<![CDATA[
<p>It wasn't reading <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flowers_in_the_Attic"><em>Flowers in the Attic</em></a> or all those <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stephen_King_bibliography"><em>Stephen King</em></a> books at too young an age that messed me up for decades, it was that damned <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Giving_Tree"><em>The Giving Tree</em></a>. *shakes fist* Damn you, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shel_Silverstein">Shel Silverstein</a>!</p>

